{"tid":140482,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"靠大隻冧麥明詩　運動狂熱分子張存華","createTime":"2017-03-02T08:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T12:54:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":27,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2088a4c98568425c703bc8b6b461d3a585ada54","tid":140482,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHZEQyS2YyaTZqUkk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHZEQyS2YyaTZqUkk&h=186c852a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n格仔餅（六嚿腹肌）是怎樣練成的，睇 Emil輕易做到引體上升便略知一二。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>靠大隻冧麥明詩　運動狂熱分子張存華</strong><br />\n<br />\n鐵板神算董慕節的外孫張存華（ Emil Cheung）是運動員經理人，又是樂視籃球評述員，以往只在體育版出沒，直至本月初，同十優港姐麥明詩於淺水灣短敍斷正，被指同林作拗手瓜爭女後， Emil旋即成為娛樂版新貴。<br />\n<br />\n練得格仔餅（六嚿腹肌）跟身，兼手瓜起𦟌，平時又愛下廚煮幾味，冧女必殺技有齊， Emil不諱言所作的一切全為了他的最愛&mdash;&mdash;籃球！反高潮吧！但當事人說起來雙眼發光，大抵這就是外間所指的運動癡！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一股傻勁</strong><br />\n<br />\nEmil愛運動愛到一個點，先是放棄金融策劃的高薪厚職，跑去做一個人工差一大截的體育記者，之後番書仔遇上汕頭大學籃球隊聘請營運總監，即使事前未實地視察過環境，合作協議都未簽，便一股傻勁拎住行李跑上位於揭陽的汕頭大學。每朝七點開會，一星期二十小時訓練，遇上飲食唔啱口味和居住環境惡劣到不能開窗通風的情況下，仍為球隊打點一年半，直到獵頭公司挖角到 Adidas Group才離開。「上到去我覺得係一個好好磨練，體育係我一個夢，我覺得有熱誠我係 live到，我應該幫有需要幫助嘅人。」 Emil雙眼有火地說。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHZG9zTEowclBBSnM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHZG9zTEowclBBSnM&h=a07ebe8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHY3YtcmVwdS1JUHM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHY3YtcmVwdS1JUHM&h=bd2c9009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自小是籃球校隊的 Emil，在美國讀大學時，曾帶領校隊鍊贏白人，成為聯賽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHWm1WSFQ2UDlveDg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHWm1WSFQ2UDlveDg&h=b04b6609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本月初於淺水灣與麥明詩短敍斷正，事後 Emil大讚對方叻女、有吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHazlxbnFSck1iejQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHazlxbnFSck1iejQ&h=1d905f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEmil同時為樂視 NBA球賽擔任評述。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHdDl1TWVGWWpKMmM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHdDl1TWVGWWpKMmM&h=abe2fbe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛食更愛下廚的 Emil，每星期都會下廚試煮新菜，其中，自家製叉燒是他的拿手小菜。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我唔大隻</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHZHJiRjRZSmhNY28\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHZHJiRjRZSmhNY28&h=be088c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙臂手瓜起𦟌，但 Emil非常抗拒俾人叫大隻仔。<br />\n<br />\n在樂視兼任 NBA評述的張存華，不介意外間稱呼他「講波佬」，表示只要球迷認同他的專業便足夠。反而對於「大隻仔」的稱號抗拒至極。見 Emil操到手瓜起𦟌，忍不住問：「係咪食大隻奶粉㗎！」對方眉頭一皺說：「我唔係操到好大隻，我目標係打籃球 OK，唔受傷同埋健康囉&hellip;&hellip;我唔會食嗰啲（大隻）奶粉。」<br />\n<br />\n為了夠體力打波兼減低受傷， Emil一星期抽六日分組做高、中、低強度運動各兩組，其中高強度運動，會請教練為自己進行訓練。「我都希望有個叻人去 push我，最少（做）一個半鐘。」 Emil說。工作忙從來都不是 Emil的藉口，即使檔期排到滿，只要有半小時， Emil都會踩上跑步機走轉，當減壓。擁有健身教練牌的他還分享了一個保持靚身形的貼士，表示晚上謝絕碳水化合物，配合少鹽、少糖的飲食習慣，配合帶氧訓練減低脂肪比例，全身的線條便會很明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>嗌救命</strong><br />\n<br />\n在 Adidas Group為另一品牌打造一支 team reebok籃球隊後， Emil被挖角到一間專責香港運動員的公關公司做市場經理，積極發掘不同範疇合作的 Emil，今個月初同十優港姐麥明詩會面斷正，外界直至他同林作拗手瓜，原本滔滔不絕的 Emil，一提到 Louisa（麥之洋名）即時嗌救命：「嘩，好驚喎，你咁樣問我，唔知點答喎真係！」<br />\n<br />\nEmil直言不會因為被傳媒撞破，而避見 Louisa，但表明現階段兩人只是朋友，不想對未來作任何猜測，但係都不忘大讚麥明詩叻女又有吸引力，冧到出面。咪睇 Emil有家底，又有齊暖男具備的條件，應該大把女埋身，實質他的感情生活已經有幾年的空窗期， Emil不否認對拍拖中的另一半有一定要求，令對方造成壓力，所以現階段不作他想，只專注工作。「我覺得呢樣嘢好隨緣，尤其姻緣好多時係注定，我媽咪同老闆成日同我講，你做嘢啦，做好啲，真係識人或者被識嘅機會係多啲，咁我希望呢刻都係專注工作。」 Emil說。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHaHB0aFBQNEFLRGs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHaHB0aFBQNEFLRGs&h=ed72853f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40b1effa38ac6d18bccf309c89fce2d34c37d3ce","tid":140482,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"再三追問同麥明詩的發展可能， Emil大嗌救命，叫記者放過佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHZFZUd1BSM1RwdGM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHZFZUd1BSM1RwdGM&h=0b9b91a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上週六同 Emil前後腳出席同一活動的林作，反口唔肯同「情敵」合照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHQnByTWthbnhOeUE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHQnByTWthbnhOeUE&h=1b90fa5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金牌運動員傅園慧來港， Emil把握機會成功集郵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHZjZCdldoZXFleVU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHZjZCdldoZXFleVU&h=e6893811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工作、運動兩忙， Emil不時會去做冷凍療程，以過百度的零下低溫紓緩疲勞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHSlR0dTJJU0V0TWc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHSlR0dTJJU0V0TWc&h=2f453d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年 Emil還擔任甲二籃球晉裕的主教練。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>張存華簡介</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B_nYHg8IFMDHdWs3ZWtrWEJDY2c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D0B_nYHg8IFMDHdWs3ZWtrWEJDY2c&h=4b54b3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從美國返港後， Emil曾在汕頭逗留一年為汕頭大學擔任營運總監。<br />\n<br />\n英文名： Emil<br />\n<br />\n年齡： 27歲<br />\n<br />\n感情狀況：單身<br />\n<br />\n背景：鐵板神算「董半仙」董慕節外孫<br />\n<br />\n學歷：美國普渡大學（ Purdue University）畢業，主修金融策劃<br />\n<br />\n事業：<br />\n<br />\n2013-14　 nowTV體育主持<br />\n<br />\n2014-15　受聘汕頭大學籃球隊營運總監<br />\n<br />\n2015-16　 Reebok市場營銷，以及香港甲二組別晉裕籃球隊主教練<br />\n<br />\n2016至今　 Harvest Sky公關顧問及樂視 NBA評述及節目主持<br />\n<br />\n撰文、攝影、攝錄：娛樂組<br />\n<br />\n來源 source: <a href=\"http://hk.next.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bc2282fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com&h=8070474f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.next.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n<br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++"},{"pid":"db8adb9ba034b0c7766913ed6de67a5e3b2fc51c","tid":140482,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81a15aeabfa23a257e91d58c2d866fd2ef876ef","tid":140482,"uid":31423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"Email Cheung"},{"pid":"f693bdd27af76bd469551d3bb4a26c0ce45d8f57","tid":140482,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"好過林作好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1d01db6c4734eab67ca6ed53818e84e6bb4ebf","tid":140482,"uid":60153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bb87a69bc38024eaf6c2f6303b12da2037278bd","tid":140482,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"算唔算男神?<br />\n識煮野食已經好大優勢"},{"pid":"62dea4cebd56114245f722d607ea71c345a7ad64","tid":140482,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"睇佢揀男朋友既眼光，對佢有d改觀"},{"pid":"c3b6066d0a2eb0423a044447c2ffb35ef57f295b","tid":140482,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e54cef3f1d1db315d58c6ad8678fc372ea04981"